				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-07-16T00:33:07.101929+02:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "78Kv5FeSSYOWivZarZNkxA=="
				},
				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "La instalación es la misma disciplina que aprendimos con el split (allí está explicada al detalle): BPLEN fuera para que el fondo se vea limpio, COPEN fuera mientras se cambia el puntero — COP1LC son dos words y el blanking vertical no espera a nadie — y COPEN de vuelta. Tras el snippet, la pantalla del Amiga son tres rasterbars sobre negro."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "pharoSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"createTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-07-16T00:33:18.551588+02:00"
					}
				},
				"editEmail" : {
					"__type" : "email",
					"emailString" : "<unknown>"
				},
				"editTime" : {
					"__type" : "time",
					"time" : {
						"__type" : "dateAndTime",
						"dateAndTimeString" : "2026-07-16T00:33:18.551588+02:00"
					}
				},
				"uid" : {
					"__type" : "uid",
					"uidString" : "rSLLPLXtS/aBqC55bv/l2Q=="
				},
				"code" : "\"Paso 2: instalar. BPLEN off, COPEN off, COP1LCH/L, COPEN on.\"\n| monitor clist |\nmonitor := GT4AmigaMonitorClient default.\nclist := Smalltalk at: #GT4ABarsList.\n{ 16rDFF096 -> 16r0100.\n  16rDFF096 -> 16r0080.\n  16rDFF080 -> (clist bitShift: -16).\n  16rDFF082 -> (clist bitAnd: 16rFFFF).\n  16rDFF096 -> 16r8080 }\n\tdo: [ :par |\n\t\t(monitor writeMemoryAt: par key size: 2 value: par value)\n\t\t\tifFalse: [ ^ 'ack perdido escribiendo ' , par key printStringHex , ' — reevalúa este snippet' ] ].\n'rasterbars en pantalla — mira el Amiga'"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
